<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.3.5">
<l>tīmaṉat tarakkar tiṟalaḻit tavaṉē yeṉṟuceṉ ṟaṭaintavar tamakkut</l>
<l>tāymaṉat tiraṅki yaruḷiṉaik koṭukkun tayarataṉ matalaiyaic cayamē</l>
<l>tēmalarp poḻilcūḻ nāṅkainaṉ ṉaṭuvuḷ cempoṉcey kōyili ṉuḷḷē,</l>
<l>kāmaṉaip payantāṉ ṟaṉṉainā ṉaṭiyēṉ kaṇṭukoṇ ṭuyntoḻin tēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, his servant, having seen for myself, within the Cempoṉcey Temple</l>
<l>Right in the center of Nānkai, encircled by groves</l>
<l rend="indent">with a multitude of honeyed blossoms,</l>
<l>Daśaratha’s son who, empathizing with a mother’s heart, grants his grace</l>
<l rend="indent">to those who take refuge,</l>
<l>Approaching [him] saying, “He is the one who destroyed the courage</l>
<l rend="indent">of the demons with evil hearts,” him who begot Kāma,</l>
<l rend="indent">being saved, I was at ease.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
